_:N9a638c1e81714a2186f960ff787ad5c5 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Alex Chisholm became Chief Operating Officer for the Civil Service and Permanent Secretary for the Cabinet Office in April 2020. Prior to that he was the Permanent Secretary to the Department for Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy (BEIS).</p>\n\n<p>Previous roles in government:</p>\n\n<p>Permanent Secretary, BEIS 2016 to 2020</p>\n\n<p>Joint Permanent Secretary, BEIS 2016 to 2016</p>\n\n<p>Permanent Secretary, DECC 2016 to 2016</p>\n\n<p>Chief Executive of the Competition and Markets Authority 2013 to 2016</p>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
